				{page_info.subtitle}
			</Description>

			<Countdown end="2025-10-20T21:59:00" start="2025-10-12T00:00:00" form_url="https://sitcon.org/" />

			<Schedule schedule={schedule} calendarUrl="https://sitcon.org/" />

			<Content title="議程早鳥">
				<ContentFormat>
					<MdContent />
				</ContentFormat>
			</Content>

			<Content title="議程種類">
				<div></div>
				<!-- TODO: blocks -->
			</Content>

			<Content title="投稿主題範例">
				<ContentFormat>
					<MdContent />

					<!-- Links start -->
					<h3>PRESENTATION</h3>
					<div class="links">
						{
							presentation_content.map(item => {
								return (
									<a class="link-item" href={item.href}>
										<img class="link-img" src={item.img} alt="HTML5" />
										<span>{item.title}</span>
									</a>
								);
							})
						}
					</div>

					<h3>ESPRESSO</h3>

					<div class="links">
						{
							espresso_content.map(item => {
								return (
									<a class="link-item" href={item.href}>
										<img class="link-img" src={item.img} alt="HTML5" />
										<span>{item.title}</span>
									</a>
								);
							})
						}
					</div>
				</ContentFormat>
			</Content>

			<div>
				<Content title="投稿格式"> 各議程類型的投稿格式相同，除標示為公開之資訊會對外公布外，其餘僅供審稿委員於審稿時閱讀。 </Content>
				<FieldDescription title="投稿欄位說明" content={field_content} />
				<PersonalInfo title="個人資料" description="除了暱稱 / 名字被用於宣傳，其餘資訊僅需提供一人作為代表（當稿件同時有多位講者時），供議程組於聯絡時使用。" content={field_content} />
			</div>

			<ContentFormat>
				<MdContent />
			</ContentFormat>

			<QA content={qa_content} />
		</div>
		<div class="banner">
			<Banner />
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		height: 100vh;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 4fr;
		grid-template-rows: auto auto;
	}

	.links {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.link-img {
		width: 100%;
		min-height: 3rem;
		height: auto;
		object-fit: contain;
	}

	.link-item {
		max-height: 14rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: #c4c4c4;
		align-items: center;
		border-radius: 1.25rem;
		background: #394877;
		padding: 1rem;
	}

	.banner {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.container {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0 3rem;
	}

	.toc {
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}
</style>
